Package: reqguard
Version: 0.3.19
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, nftables | ufw
Maintainer: reqguard maintainers
Description: Terminal network request monitor with firewall IP banning
 reqguard monitors inbound TCP connections from a terminal UI and can persist
 and apply IP bans through ufw or nftables before traffic reaches local web
 services.
